prediction.sparql:
PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?team ?teamName WHERE {
  fb:m.095xk6 fb:people.person.education ?education .
  ?education fb:education.education.institution fb:m.01vs5c .
  ?team fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team fb:m.0g0z58 .
  ?team fb:sports.sports_team_roster.player fb:m.095xk6 .
  fb:m.0g0z58 rdfs:label ?teamName .
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  fb:m.02m29p fb:film.film_character.portrayed_in_films ?performance .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.special_performance_type fb:m.02nsjvf .
  ?actor rdfs:label ?actorName .
  FILTER ( lang( ?actorName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?team ?teamName WHERE {
  fb:m.05cb70 fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?teamRoster .
  ?teamRoster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?team rdfs:label ?teamName .
    FILTER ( lang( ?teamName ) = "en" )
  }
  ?teamRoster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.from ?startDate .
  ?teamRoster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.to ?endDate .
  FILTER ( ( ?startDate <= "2011-12-31" ^^ xsd:date || ?startDate <= "2011" ^^ xsd:gYear ) && ( ?endDate >= "2011-01-01" ^^ xsd:date || ?endDate >= "2011" ^^ xsd:gYear ) )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  fb:m.01s3vk fb:film.film.starring ?performance .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?actor fb:type.object.name ?actorName .
  ?performance fb:film.performance.character ?character .
  ?character fb:type.object.name "Edward Scissorhands" @en .
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?place ?placeLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0g7km1 fb:people.person.places_lived ?place .
  ?place fb:people.place_lived.location ?location .
  ?location rdfs:label ?placeLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?placeLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?championship ?championshipLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0j6tr fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship rdfs:label ?championshipLabel .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?championshipLabel ) , "1963 stanley cup finals" ) )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?genreLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.01s21dg fb:music.artist.genre ?genre .
  ?genre rdfs:label ?genreLabel
  FILTER ( lang( ?genreLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?anthemName WHERE {
  fb:m.0d060g fb:location.country.national_anthem ?anthem .
  ?anthem fb:government.national_anthem_of_a_country.anthem ?anthemEntity .
  ?anthemEntity rdfs:label ?anthemName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?anthemName ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?work ?workLabel ?dateOfFirstPublication WHERE {
  fb:m.026v43 rdfs:label ?workLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?workLabel ) = "en" ) .
  fb:m.026v43 fb:book.written_work.date_of_first_publication ?dateOfFirstPublication
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?person ?personName WHERE {
  ?position fb:government.government_office_or_title.office_holders ?officeHolder .
  ?officeHolder fb:government.government_position_held.office_holder ?person .
  ?officeHolder fb:government.government_position_held.from ?startDate .
  ?officeHolder fb:government.government_position_held.to ?endDate .
  ?person rdfs:label ?personName .
  FILTER ( ?startDate <= "1993-12-31" ^^ xsd:date && ?endDate >= "1993-01-01" ^^ xsd:date ) FILTER ( ?position = fb:m.060m4 )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?college ?collegeLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.01_fz1 fb:people.person.education ?education .
  ?education fb:education.education.institution ?college .
  ?college rdfs:label ?collegeLabel .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?collegeLabel ) , "university" ) )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?teamName WHERE {
  fb:m.03yx01 fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  ?team fb:type.object.name ?teamName .
  FILTER ( ?team IN ( fb:m.07l24 , fb:m.06rny ) )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ?team ?teamName WHERE {
  fb:m.02d9k fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?roster .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  OPTIONAL {
    ?team fb:type.object.name ?teamName
  }
  .
  ?roster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.to ?to .
  FILTER ( ?to < "2007" ^^ xsd:gYear )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?to )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?team ?teamName WHERE {
  fb:m.0h7q7b fb:sports.pro_athlete.teams ?teamRoster .
  ?teamRoster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.team ?team .
  ?team rdfs:label ?teamName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?teamName ) = "en" ) ?teamRoster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.from ?startDate .
  ?teamRoster fb:sports.sports_team_roster.to ?endDate .
  FILTER ( YEAR( ?startDate ) <= 2010 && YEAR( ?endDate ) >= 2010 )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?player ?playerName WHERE {
  ?team fb:type.object.name "Miami Dolphins" @en .
  ?team fb:sports.sports_team.roster ?rosterEntry .
  ?rosterEntry fb:sports.sports_team_roster.number "22" .
  ?rosterEntry fb:sports.sports_team_roster.player ?player .
  ?player fb:type.object.name ?playerName .
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>

  ?performance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.character fb:m.0f22p8 .
  ?performance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.series fb:m.01b64v .
  ?performance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.actor ?actor .

}
SELECT "2014" AS ?year WHERE { }

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?fatherPlaceName ?motherPlaceName WHERE {

  ?fatherPlace fb:type.object.name ?fatherPlaceName .
  fb:m.0c7vl1 fb:people.person.place_of_birth ?motherPlace .
  ?motherPlace fb:type.object.name ?motherPlaceName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?fatherPlaceName ) = "en" ) FILTER ( LANG( ?motherPlaceName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>

SELECT ?arena ?arenaLabel WHERE {

  FILTER ( LANG( ?arenaLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>

SELECT ?honor ?honorLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0ldd fb:user.alexbl.honorary_title.titled_person.honorary_title ?honor .
  ?honor rdfs:label ?honorLabel .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?honorLabel ) , "dame" ) )

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?country WHERE {
  fb:m.07hcc fb:base.ancientegypt.tomb_owner.tomb_owned ?tomb .
  ?tomb fb:location.location.containedby ?country .
  ?country fb:type.object.name ?countryName .

}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?college ?collegeLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0c2yrf fb:people.person.education ?education .
  ?education fb:education.education.institution ?college .
  ?college rdfs:label ?collegeLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?collegeLabel ) = "en" ) FILTER ( ?college = fb:m.0j_sncb )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?title WHERE {
  fb:m.09b6zr fb:book.author.works_written ?book .
  ?book fb:type.object.name ?title .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?title ) , "decision points" ) )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?description ?notableTypeLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0btx2g fb:common.topic.description ?description .
  fb:m.0btx2g fb:common.topic.notable_types ?notableType .
  ?notableType rdfs:label ?notableTypeLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?description ) = "en" ) FILTER ( LANG( ?notableTypeLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  fb:m.0gynx fb:film.film_character.portrayed_in_films ?filmPerformance .
  ?filmPerformance fb:film.performance.actor ?actor .
  ?actor fb:type.object.name ?actorName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?actorName ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?region ?regionLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.05kkh fb:location.location.containedby ?region .
  ?region rdfs:label ?regionLabel .
  FILTER ( ?region IN ( fb:m.02jwvm , fb:m.03pzys ) ) FILTER ( lang( ?regionLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.01d6g fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship rdfs:label ?championshipLabel .
  BIND( REPLACE( STR( ?championshipLabel ) , ".*([0-9]{4}).*" , "$1" ) AS ?year ) .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?championshipLabel ) , "world series" ) )
}
ORDER BY ?year

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?product ?description WHERE {
  fb:m.0lwkh fb:business.consumer_company.products ?productRel .
  ?productRel fb:business.company_product_relationship.consumer_product ?product .
  ?product fb:common.topic.description ?description .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?description ) = "en" )
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?actor ?actorName WHERE {
  ?performance fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.character fb:m.035szd ; fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.seasons fb:m.027gynh ; fb:tv.regular_tv_appearance.actor ?actor .
  ?actor rdfs:label ?actorName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?actorName ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?championship ?championshipLabel WHERE {
  fb:m.0jmfb fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship rdfs:label ?championshipLabel .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?championshipLabel ) , "1994" ) )
}
LIMIT 1

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?coach ?coachName WHERE {
  fb:m.01y3c fb:sports.sports_team.coaches ?coachTenure .
  ?coachTenure fb:sports.sports_team_coach_tenure.coach ?coach .
  ?coach rdfs:label ?coachName .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?coachName ) = "en" )
}
ORDER BY ?coachName

PREFIX fb: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT ?year WHERE {
  fb:m.0713r fb:sports.sports_team.championships ?championship .
  ?championship fb:type.object.name ?name .
  ?championship fb:time.event.start_date ?startDate .
  FILTER ( CONTAINS( LCASE( ?name ) , "world series" ) ) BIND( YEAR( ?startDate ) AS ?year )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?startDate )
LIMIT 1
